couldn't go on as planned.

15
00:01:07,112 --> 00:01:08,029
I'm very sorry.

16
00:01:23,545 --> 00:01:24,379
Hello?

17
00:01:24,462 --> 00:01:26,631
Hey, you're up. Did you sleep well?

18
00:01:26,715 --> 00:01:28,341
Yes. How about you?

19
00:01:28,425 --> 00:01:29,467
