I'm the one who did all the work.

67
00:05:54,774 --> 00:05:56,150
Sorry.

68
00:05:57,318 --> 00:05:58,277
Why, this…

69
00:05:58,987 --> 00:06:00,238
Your shoes…

70
00:06:00,321 --> 00:06:01,823
