128
00:09:14,682 --> 00:09:17,018
Oh, right. Get me some women's heels.

129
00:09:17,685 --> 00:09:18,644
The size

130
00:09:19,729 --> 00:09:20,730
should be 230.

131
00:09:20,813 --> 00:09:23,274
