all of a sudden?

132
00:09:23,357 --> 00:09:24,192
Who are they for?

133
00:09:26,736 --> 00:09:27,945
My girlfriend.

134
00:09:28,029 --> 00:09:29,405
Girlfriend?

135
00:09:30,281 --> 00:09:31,115
No way.

136
00:09:35,661 --> 00:09:36,871
Is Ms. Shin Ha-ri here?

137
00:09:37,497 --> 00:09:38,539
