138
00:09:40,249 --> 00:09:41,375
What is it?

139
00:09:41,459 --> 00:09:43,628
Your boyfriend sent you a gift.

140
00:09:43,711 --> 00:09:44,962
Boyfriend?

141
00:09:50,384 --> 00:09:51,719
Could you sign here?

142
00:10:00,269 --> 00:10:03,314
What is it?

143
00:10:04,273 --> 00:10:06,192
