145
00:10:08,903 --> 00:10:10,404
Let's see.

146
00:10:10,988 --> 00:10:12,490
What? They're heels.

147
00:10:13,074 --> 00:10:16,118
Right! You've been upset today
because you wore mismatched shoes.

148
00:10:16,202 --> 00:10:19,413
