236
00:15:20,297 --> 00:15:23,926
<i>Mr. Cha, are you busy?
Why aren't you checking my texts?</i>

237
00:15:24,009 --> 00:15:26,345
<i>Please text me back.</i>

238
00:15:26,428 --> 00:15:28,889
<i>Please?</i>

239
00:15:30,432 --> 00:15:33,686
<i>I thought I ended things that day,
so why is she doing this?</i>

240
00:15:36,564 --> 00:15:39,191
