that he wishes to marry.

241
00:15:40,192 --> 00:15:41,110
I'm very sorry.

242
00:15:41,193 --> 00:15:43,904
Oh, my god.

243
00:15:45,322 --> 00:15:47,867
This is destiny.

244
00:15:47,950 --> 00:15:49,159
It's fate.

245
00:15:49,243 --> 00:15:50,160
What?

246
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:52,037
